{"about_the_game":"<strong>&quot;Santa's Busy Day&quot;</strong> is an<i> atmospheric little arcade game</i>. You control Santa's sleigh and <strong>fly</strong> over roofs, trees, churches, and more. The goal is to <strong>drop</strong> presents at the right time, so they fall into the right place.<br><br>There are two modes in this game:<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2723640/extras/Competitive_Mode.png?t=1703323387\" /><br><br><br><strong>Compete</strong> with players around the world. Who can drop <strong>the most</strong> presents without crashing into a building? This mode will get progressively <u>harder</u> and <u>faster</u>.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2723640/extras/Relaxed_Mode.png?t=1703323387\" /><br><br><br>For everyone who wants to enjoy the <i>peace</i> and <i>atmosphere</i> of Christmas. It's <strong>specifically designed</strong> to be relaxing. There's no score, and it doesn't get faster \u2013 just for you to enjoy.<br><br>If you're not yet in a Christmas mood, <u>maybe you will</u> be because of this game. <strong>That's our goal.</strong>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2723640/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1703323387","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2723640/page.bg.jpg?t=1703323387","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2723640/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1703323387","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2723640/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1703323387","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<strong>&quot;Santa's Busy Day&quot;</strong> is an<i> atmospheric little arcade game</i>. You control Santa's sleigh and <strong>fly</strong> over roofs